The '''North Garden''' was a part of [[Monument Plaza/Legends|Monument Plaza]]. [[Nenevanth Tion]] gave a speech to 6,000 members of [[SAGroup (COMPOR)/Legends|SAGroup]] there in [[21 BBY/Legends|21 BBY]], celebrating the victories of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] in the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

